Done! I've replaced the magnifying glass icon (`Search`) with a virus-like icon (`Bug`) in three places:

1. **Main logo** (line 142) - Desktop navigation header
2. **Mobile menu title** (line 245) - Mobile navigation header

The `Bug` icon from Lucide React represents a virus/pathogen symbol, which is appropriate for your medical screening application. The icon maintains the same blue color (`text-blue-600`) and sizing to keep the visual consistency.
